home.title: Welcome to Let it jump!
home.subtitle: Here you can consult all you want of this Android game
home.explanation:
Let it jump is a platform game for the Android operating system. It was created as an idea final work CFGS Cross-Platform Application Development of five STUCOM students.
In this section you will find several things, among them: a world ranking with the best players, a page with the history of the characters of the world of Let it jump, as well as a section to manage your account.
Said this, feel free to discover web features.
Greetings.
home.subexplanation:
* The page is still under construction. Some sections are missing and most are not finished. Feel free to comment on new errors both in the game and on this website.
Our email is letitjump.help@gmail.com. We appreciate your help.
